description: Project team 4 for CSE 210, fall 2022. Daniela Perry, Qiwen Zhao, Satvik Gupta, Dev Gulati, Shicheng Bei, Teja Dhondu, Xiang Lu. Project repo for ProdoType, a social pomodoro timer app. We present ProdoType, an app for tracking and sharing your productivity throughout the day.
